    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT340-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">iravukkuṟi uṇarttiya tōḻikkuk kiḻatti maṟuttatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">SHE refused the confidante, who announced night trysts. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT340">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> kāmaṅ kaṭaiyiṟ kātalarp paṭarntu</l>
          <l> nāmavarp pulampi ṉammō ṭāki</l>
          <l> yorupāṟ paṭutal cellā tāyiṭai</l>
          <l> yaḻuva niṉṟa valarvēy kaṇṭal</l>
          <l> kaḻipeyar maruṅki ṉolki yōtam</l>
          <l> peyartarap peyartan tāṅku</l>
          <l> varuntun tōḻiyava riruntaveṉ ṉeñcē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>At a time it set out for the lover, when desire increased,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">[and] was with us, when we lamented him,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">without [however] going to share one [single] fate ,</l>
          <l>my heart that was with him , is troubled, friend,</l>
          <l rend="indent">like the flood moving [just] to move [again] </l>
          <l rend="indent">[and] becoming weak on the side where the backwaters stir</l>
          <l rend="indent2">with blossom-covered mangroves standing in the depth.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
